<statement>
<p>Solve this system of equations using substitution.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}-{9}{y}={33}</m> </p>
<p>
  <m>\displaystyle-{6}{x}+{8}{y}=-{66}</m></p>
<p><fillin characters="8"/></p>

</statement>
<solution>
<p><ul><li><m>\displaystyle{\left({3},-{6}\right)}</m></li></ul></p><p>We chose (for no special reason) to solve the first equation for <m>\displaystyle{x}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}+-{9}{y}={33}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}={33}-{\left(-{9}{y}\right)}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=\frac{{{33}-{\left(-{9}{y}\right)}}}{{-{{7}}}}</m></p>
<p>Then we can substitute this into the second equation.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{6}{\left(\frac{{{33}-{\left(-{9}{y}\right)}}}{{-{{7}}}}\right)}+{8}{y}=-{66}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-\frac{{6}}{{-{{7}}}}\cdot{\left({33}\right)}--\frac{{6}}{{-{{7}}}}{\left(-{9}\right)}{y}+{8}{y}=-{66}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{28.285714285714}-{\left({7.7142857142857}\right)}{y}+{8}{y}=-{66}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{7.7142857142857}{y}+{\left({8}\right)}{y}=-{66}-{28.285714285714}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{7.7142857142857}{y}+{\left({8}\right)}{y}=-{94.285714285714}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{\left({7.7142857142857}+{\left({8}\right)}\right)}{y}=-{94.285714285714}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{15.714285714286}{y}=-{94.285714285714}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{y}=-\frac{{94.285714285714}}{{15.714285714286}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{y}=-{6}</m></p>
<p>Finally we can substitute this y value into the first equation to solve for x.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}+-{9}{\left(-{6}\right)}={33}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}+{\left({54}\right)}={33}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}={33}-{\left({54}\right)}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle-{7}{x}=-{21}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=-\frac{{21}}{{-{{7}}}}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}={3}</m></p>
<p>Thus the answer is <m>\displaystyle{\left({3},-{6}\right)}</m>.</p>

</solution>
